relation: Darrow1 - #09 While the events may have jumped a bit, Pokey eventually makes his appearance! While Ness is rather passive aggressive, Paula is definitely not one to put up with Pokey's rude behavior. They'd almost make a good duo if it...weren't for the whole evil thing.

Darrow1 - #10 Arriving home, Paula meets with her parents one last time before her big adventure. Unfortunately, Paula's dad is too awesome to be able to come along...but there is a brief mention of Jeff! Are you excited? I'm excited.

Darrow1 - #11 Everdred, who is definitely not a crook, casually passes off a wad of cash to Ness and Paula, who realize they can't actually spend any of it. Too bad they never learned how to do the Egg/Chicken trick. They would be set for life.
Darrow1 - #12 Oh boy! It's a date to the Chaos Theater. Thanks to the ongoing contract battle between the Runaway Five and ol Poochyfud, backstage passes are currently going for $0. Yay!
Darrow1 - #13 Poochyfud lays down the law, although his time in the spotlight has yet to come. For now, Ness and Paula have more important things to attend to. Like keeping their bodies intact.
